[I] A flexible distributed key-value datastore

[T] Valkey is a high-performance data structure server that primarily serves
[T] key/value workloads. It supports a wide range of native structures and an
[T] extensible plugin system for adding new data structures and access patterns.

[U] https://valkey.io

